comments: Curry (GSW) draws Williams (BOS) towards him and the body contact results in a shooting foul on Williams even if contact is initiated by Curry.
Green (GSW) makes incidental hand on ball contact with Brown (BOS) at the start of his drive.

Bazemore (GSW) briefly places his hand on Theis' (BOS) back and the contact is marginal before he makes clean contact with the ball.  He does not make any further contact with Theis following the contact with the ball.
Bazemore (GSW) moves laterally into Walker's (BOS) body during the drive with 1:09 remaining and the contact affects his SQBR.
Bazemore (GSW) makes contact to Tatum's (BOS) arm during the drive and the contact affects his SQBR. The contact occurs prior to Tatum's gather.
Green (GSW) commits a take foul on Williams (BOS).
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) dives to the floor in an attempt to retrieve the loose ball and makes contact to Tatum's (BOS) lower body that causes him to fall to the floor.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) makes contact with the ball and dislodges it from Tatum (BOS) during his dribble.
Toscano-Anderson (GSW) commits a take foul on Williams (BOS).
Walker (BOS) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
